title: The simpsons tapped Out v4.6.2 ult donuts + cash + ALL OLD ITEMS
description:
The Simpson tapped out, latest version January 18th. 2013.

version 4.6.2



UNLIMITED CASH
UNLIMITED DONUTS (donuts stay in your account unlike other hacks)

...then
